creator: Close BV
descriptionHtml:
Close connects you with events in new and exciting ways; before, during and after the event.

With Close you will have absolutely everything you need for the event, including your tickets, schedules, reminders, reservations and (pre-)purchases. Close is at your service, ready to inform you about the traffic, the weather and line-up changes.

MAIN FEATURES:
+ Tickets
+ Group chats
+ Offers and surprises
+ Personal assistance
+ Payments and (pre-)purchases
+ Event-themed camera filters
+ Contests and surveys

Close is free to use. The only purchases that can be made are directly connected to the event, such as tickets, merchandise, food and beverages.

Visit beclose.to for more information

title: Close

creator: Close BV
descriptionHtml:
Close connects you with events in new and exciting ways; before, during and after the event.

With Close you will have absolutely everything you need for the event, including your tickets, schedules, reminders, reservations and (pre-)purchases. Close is at your service, ready to inform you about the traffic, the weather and line-up changes.

MAIN FEATURES:
+ Tickets
+ Group chats
+ Offers and surprises
+ Personal assistance
+ Payments and (pre-)purchases
+ Event-themed camera filters
+ Contests and surveys

Close is free to use. The only purchases that can be made are directly connected to the event, such as tickets, merchandise, food and beverages.

Visit thecloseapp.com for more information!

title: Close

creator: Close BV
descriptionHtml:
With the Close app you'll visit events carefree! All your tickets, information and updates from your events in one spot.

BYE PDF, HELLO HANDY APP
For events that work with Close, you can provide your phone number when purchasing. This gives you access to the event and your digital tickets in the app. Even if you are without internet, you have your ticket(s) at hand.

EVERYTHING IS READY FOR YOU
What time do you have to be there? Where to park? Which measures apply? No stress! The app contains all relevant event information in a clear overview. Everyone in the group will receive updates and helpful reminders.

SHARE TICKETS WITH YOUR FRIENDS
You experience events together, but buying and distributing tickets is often a hassle. With Close you can easily share tickets with friends by inviting them to your group via a special link. Made a mistake? Don't worry, you're still in charge.

ENJOY THE ANTICIPATION TOGETHER
Thanks to the app, you literally get closer to the event. Be surprised with nice messages from the organizer and chat with your group. With Close you will be prepared! Messages you send to each other are not visible to Close nor the event.

DISCOVER EVENTS AND GET OUT AND ABOUT
An empty agenda? Close offers you a selection of cool events to discover. This is the place where you will be challenged for your next adventure with your group. Have fun!
descriptionShort: The app for all your events

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Close is constantly improving services to take care of your events!

In this version of the app, we especially worked on:
An improved view for having multiple events, with a separation between events that are still on your calendar and those that ended. This way you will quickly find what you are looking for and in the long run build a nice overview of your attended events!
